pending on this quarter=E2=80=99s earnings). But even outside of those=C2=
=A0mechanical requirements, you get people saying stuff like this:</p><bloc=
kquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Nicholas Colas, co-founder of DataTrek =
Research, said he thought the S&amp;P index committee would be leery of put=
ting GameStop or any other so-called meme stock in the S&amp;P 500.</p><p s=
tyle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The biggest reason? =E2=80=9CIts valuation isn=E2=
=80=99t supported by fundamentals,=E2=80=9D Mr. Colas said. ...</p><p style=
=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ultimately, the index committee would probably want to=
 see GameStop prove it can maintain its market capitalization for a longer =
stretch of time before seriously considering the stock for inclusion in the=
